ABB Is Selected to Provide High-Voltage $900 Million Power Link in India

-- B y   M a t t h i a s   W a b l
-- 
2011-03-23T10:32:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-23/abb-is-selected-to-provide-high-voltage-900-million-power-link-in-india.html
  ABB Ltd. (ABBN)  has been selected by the
Power Grid Corporation of  India  Ltd. to deliver an ultrahigh-
voltage transmission system, worth about $900 million. The link
will supply hydropower from northeastern India to the city of
Agra over a distance of 1,728 kilometers.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Matthias Wabl at 
 mwabl@bloomberg.net  